&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience owning regional event strategy and execution, including Tier 2 and Tier 3 events, field programs, executive experiences, partner events, and industry-specific demand generation activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of how to build field marketing programs that support both new logo acquisition and pipeline acceleration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving and analytical skills, with the ability to use data to measure and optimize campaign performance, event impact, partner contribution, and ROI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong cross-functional leadership skills, with the ability to build alignment across Sales, Partner Marketing, Channel, Demand Generation, Product Marketing, and Sales Engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
