&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Apply Now?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Sumo Logic, we believe the best teams are built before the hiring starts. If you&#39;re &lt;strong&gt;curious about what&#39;s next&lt;/strong&gt; in your career—even if you&#39;re not actively job hunting—we invite you to join our talent network. Submitting your profile now means you&#39;ll be &lt;strong&gt;first in line&lt;/strong&gt; when the right opportunity opens.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll stay on our radar for roles that match your expertise in &lt;strong&gt;cloud-native engineering, distributed systems, data security or observability&lt;/strong&gt;—and we’ll reach out when the timing aligns.&lt;/p&gt;
